## Calculate $R^2$ {.smaller}


::: {.cell output-location='column-fragment'}

```{.r .cell-code}
ss_fit <- sum(b_cs$.resid^2)

ss_null <- sum(
  (b_cs$tot_cholesterol - avg_c)^2
)
```
:::


$R^2 = 1 - \displaystyle \frac {SS_{fit}}{SS_{null}}$


::: {.cell output-location='column-fragment'}

```{.r .cell-code}
rsq <- 1 - ss_fit / ss_null
rsq
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 0.1837759
```


:::
:::


